IMAPAccount hackstling
Host imap.dreamhost.com
User info@hackstling.com
PassCmd "pass email/hackstling"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore hackstling-remote
Account hackstling

MaildirStore hackstling-local
Path ~/.mail/hackstling/
Inbox ~/.mail/hackstling/Inbox

Channel hackstling
Master :hackstling-remote:
Slave :hackstling-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *

